WEBVTT

00:00:29.836 --> 00:00:32.857
She'd be staring at nothing in particular.

00:00:33.633 --> 00:00:37.387
I'd watch her slowly climb the stairs,

00:00:37.411 --> 00:00:39.662
and she wasn't the mom I grew up with.

00:00:40.053 --> 00:00:43.418
I saw, instead, a frail,

00:00:43.442 --> 00:00:47.109
tiny, old woman.

00:00:49.339 --> 00:00:52.875
A few weeks went by,
and I needed a break from my painting.

00:00:52.899 --> 00:00:55.557
I wanted to play with the new camera
I had just bought.

00:00:55.581 --> 00:00:58.970
I was excited --
it had all sorts of dials,

00:00:58.994 --> 00:01:01.319
buttons and settings I wanted to learn,